  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1689310/extras/f063abd4ef4481aa128a10eecda64c98.avif?t=1662893327\" width=610 height=226 /></span><br><br>The story of Bill Bear is a visual novel with platformer elements, in which you have to help a lost teddy bear to return to its young owner.<br>Adventures, dangers, and new friends are waiting for the hero on such a long, for his little paws, way home.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1689310/extras/1f28dc9e8232d010ae7badd9abf2cc8b.poster.avif?t=1662893327\" width=610 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1689310/extras/1f28dc9e8232d010ae7badd9abf2cc8b.webm?t=1662893327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1689310/extras/1f28dc9e8232d010ae7badd9abf2cc8b.mp4?t=1662893327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In this game you are waiting for:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>gameplay that combines the mechanics of a platformer and a visual novel<br></li><li>unexpected plot twists<br></li><li>charming characters<br></li><li>a touching story</li></ul>If you cried at Toy Story, then before you sit down for Little Bear, we advise you to stock up on handkerchiefs in advance!",
